[Civil No. 821.] THE CITY OF PRESCOTT, Appellant, v. T. C. HILL, Appellee. APPEAL from the District Court of the Fourth Judicial District in and for the County of Yavapai. R. E. Sloan, Judge. ' J. H. Collins, for Appellant. Ross & O’Sullivan, for Appellee. January 15, 1903.

Dismissed on short transcript under paragraph 1583 of the Revised Statutes 'of Arizona, 1901.
